{"tid":1240332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6.21唔會有人出","createTime":"2019-06-18T10:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T12:37:19.000Z","uid":12970,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e2cdc09dbc92a93521be59eebbbfb325f5c018","tid":1240332,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:10:05.000Z","msg":"我屌啦仲有三日<br />\n熱門一個行動相關嘅po都冇<br />\n文宣又冇人傳開去<br />\n行動內容又冇人講<br />\n唔好話多唔多人三罷<br />\n我驚啲人連有三罷都唔知<br />\n唔好話遊行人數會唔會再多過上次<br />\n連連登圍內都冇乜人討論<br />\n我就睇下幾多大眾市民會企出黎喇今次<br />\n大家咪繼續開po笑鳩人地割蓆同打飛機囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講我仲以為已經贏左<br />\n<br />\n不過最後唔撤回都唔緊要<br />\n可以繼續睇啲高官開記招點柒比我開心下就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1ff3a948feceef956f11491d030203aeb7c070","tid":1240332,"uid":153748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:37:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"631d5a40f999c1403d75ceac7a113ed10257a435","tid":1240332,"uid":153748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:37:19.000Z","msg":"推"}]}